  <roomsDescription><![CDATA[<p><strong>Standard Rooms</strong> sleep two to three people.  These rooms are furnished in a typical mountain style, and can be made up as a twin or triple room.</p>
<p><strong>Family Rooms</strong> sleep three to four people. These rooms are furnished in a typical mountain style and can be made up as a double or a twin, with up to two additional beds.</p>
<p>Single occupancy rooms are available on request, for a supplement. Please give our Reservations team a call to book.</p>
<p> </p>
<p><strong>Room facilities</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>Wi-Fi</li>
<li>Satellite TV</li>
